input: there was a beehive on the on the grounds and they had just roped that area off so that people would just not disturb the bees because they were migrating or something i don't know something like that huge swimming pool with a horizon edge so i've taken some gorgeous pictures let me drop one here if you want to buy a print of this let me know i'll put it on a photo site where you can get a print of that picture because it's gorgeous oh my gosh when i got back i found that my map of my town poster had arrived and so those have started selling on my website for local people. People from other areas don't need these.
offline_reference: 院子里有个蜂巢，他们刚用绳子把那片区域围起来，以免人们打扰蜜蜂，因为它们正在迁徙之类的，我也不太清楚，还有个巨大的泳池，边缘与地平线齐平，我拍了一些非常漂亮的照片，让我在这里放一张，如果你想买这张照片的印刷品，请告诉我，我会把它上传到一个摄影网站上，你可以下载打印，因为这照片实在太美了，天啊，我回来后发现我的小镇地图海报到了，现在我已经开始在网站上售卖这些给本地人，其他地区的人其实并不需要这些。
